file.name: modelWithArrayOfModel.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  schemas:
    MeterValue:
      type: object
      title: MeterValue
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
        connectorId:
          type: string
        value:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        date:
          type: string
          format: date
        createdBy:
          type: string
        createdOn:
          type: string
          format: date-time
    MeterValues:
      description: a list of meter values.
      type: array
      items:
        $ref: '#/components/schemas/MeterValue'      
      title: MeterValues
      x-tags:
          - MeterValues
